name: Enju Aihara | Black Bullet
description:
A lora based on the character Enju Aihara from Black Bullet


Use at 0.8~1.0 weights

  • Use triggerword "enjudefault" for her default yellow outfit

  • Use triggerword "enjucasual" to summon her in her hoodie + short/skirt outfit

  • Use triggerword "enjudress" for the nightdress outfit

The dataset for both the dress and casual wear were really small (80% screencap) and
might be restrained in terms of poses and environnement

The casual outfit was trained without the color tags, you can influence its colors by adding a color tag (not perfect tho)

Some output from the casual outfit might have blur effects.
Using highres.fix at minimum 1.3 should completly negate it.

Tested on :

  • Greymix

  • MidnightMelt

  • AOM3

  • Kotosmix

  • Sweetmix

  • Henssaku

  • Mandarine

If you have any questions feel free to ask.
Kaïros#4463
Enjoy ♥

modelVersions.name: v1.5
modelVersions.description: Retrained longer with a smoother approach. better quality output in general
